    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Can I ask that we leave this one be for a while, until I've got some of my IPEP2 work merged in, especially the stateful transformers in #2293?\n\nIn terms of what we use to delimit a cell, I think we should use the same rule for reading files as we do in the line-oriented frontends. At present, they accumulate a cell magic until they see an empty line - but the refactoring in #2293 will make it easier to modify that logic if we need to.\n"
